window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Three Volumes in a single offering!</b></p> <p>When the dust settles, all hell breaks loose!</p> <p>With Ravenheart defeated and his regal duties done, Josh and his lovely misfits return to their idyllic home nestled in the shadows of the Hangsane. Will they hang up their weapons, end their monster-hunting days, and settle down for a cozy slice of farming life like so many heroes?</p> <p>Absolutely not!</p> <p>Attacked, rescued, forced into the Hangsane to seek more power, Josh and the Misfits are hurled straight into the thick of it.</p> <p>Can they fight their way to the mythical ruins? What horrors will they discover?</p>"; 
